===Etymology===
Middle English and Middle French {{term|sillabe|lang=frm}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|syllaba|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|συλλαβή||sc=polytonic|tr=sullabē|lang=grc}}, from {{term|συλλαμβάνω||I gather together|sc=polytonic|tr=sullambanō|lang=grc}}, from {{term|συν|συν-|together|sc=polytonic|tr=sun-|lang=grc}} + {{term|λαμβάνω||I take|tr=lambanō|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}.

